highlights.text: Ed Sheeran has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Shape of You” is the highest at #3.
“That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 24 weeks straight.
“One Last Time” by Ariana Grande is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 89 spots at #110.
